
Manage the summon installation, including self-update and uninstall.

Usage:
  summon self [command]

Available Commands:
  uninstall   Remove summon from your system
  update      Update summon to the latest version

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for self

Global Flags:
      --no-color        Disable colored output
      --target string   Target a specific CLI: copilot or claude

Use "summon self [command] --help" for more information about a command.
